{"tid":270194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大論壇「愛國情懷到盡頭，悼念燭光為何留」全場滿座","createTime":"2017-06-04T07:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T08:04:00.000Z","uid":30807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e369e1ad403cc6217cf22c9fd7a99312859146f","tid":270194,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929363783946760&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1487928594756950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1929363783946760%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D1487928594756950&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c775db5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929363783946760&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1487928594756950</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學學生會舉辦六四廿八週年論壇「愛國情懷到盡頭，悼念燭光為何留」，現場所見，有數百人出席，全場滿座，樓梯和地板亦坐有人。學生會在論壇場地外側設電視直播，亦坐滿人。<br />\n15：03<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/152020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F152020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=005e639a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e25ff95eda4e33890929f53df7dd5a0f9249f96f","tid":270194,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"【文字直播】香港民族黨主席陳浩天，於香港大學學生會六四論壇表示，他認為要紀念的，是民主先烈的理念、先烈的崇高，不分國界。他特地覆述在天安門城樓下，向毛澤東像潑墨的「天安門三君子」事蹟，並稱向三人致敬。陳浩天又認為，悼念不應是用來發死人財。<br />\n14：55<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/152340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F152340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b91d6e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929362417280230&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1487928594756950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1929362417280230%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D1487928594756950&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b8387598\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929362417280230&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1487928594756950</a>"},{"pid":"6f49526bc354045d10d4ea9d014f26d47a80963e","tid":270194,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"efafe409ceb7f2fe75db3a4abeddda85a00a95c3","tid":270194,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:04:00.000Z","msg":","}]}